* Restart Clusters\nEnvironmental Issues
** When to Restart
***_ Resource exhaustion
***_ Malfunctioning executors
***_ Stale container images
** Before Restarting
***_ Check Event log tab
***_ Instance acquisition failures
***_ Spot instance reclamation
***_ Executor terminations
** Restart via UI
***_ Compute page
***_ Select cluster → Restart
** Restart via CLI
***_ databricks clusters restart
***_ Need cluster ID
***_ databricks clusters list
** Important Notes
***_ Terminates running jobs
***_ Resets Spark UI history
***_ Save diagnostics first
***_ Schedule streaming restarts
** After Restart
***_ Validate fix
***_ Monitor next job run
***_ Check execution times
@endmindmap
